Summary
What I understood
Date:26/03/23

A. Learning outcome...
1. What to do in Ramdan?

B. Learning outcome...
1. Avoid bad thing
2. Do more prayer
3. Read Quran
4. Give charity
5. Good deeds
6. Stop angry

1. TV dekhna, Net flex dekhna, match dekhna, ya aur bhi koi TV program dekhna, Ramzan me sab chijen band kar de.

2. Ramzan ka Mahina duaon ka Mahina hota hai, tu Ramzan mein jyada se jyada dua mange.

3. Koshish karen ki Ramzan mein jyada se jyada Quran pade.

4. Ramzan ke mahine mein aap sadka de sakte hain, logon Ko khana khila sakte hain, Pani pila sakte, aftari karva sakte hain, Jo madad ka talabgar hai uski madad kar sakte.

5. Logon ke sath achcha suluk kare, Apne bacchon, biwi, doston, rishtedar, padosiyon ke saath.

6. Ho sake to Ramzan mein gussa Na Karen, logon Ko maaf Karna sikhen, Allah rabbul izzat aapko bhi maaf kar dega.
